---
title: Easy Pulled Pork Rogan Josh Curry with Peas, Quick Rice, Naan and Yoghurt Drizzle
description: Deliciously easy to cook, it only takes 3 steps to put this Easy Pulled Pork Rogan Josh Curry on the table. Combine our chef-approved shortcuts and simple instructions to make a restaurant quality dinner that's as easy as 1-2-3!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R38_W20_UK_SRC19390-4_MAIN_low-96ff5264.jpg
